Quickstrike:



"What?" He wasn't pleased with this change. It was no good. One bot 
dies who thinks she's leader and bots with no commanding experience 
jump in.

He turned to Drill Bit and fired at his chest.

"There's no way these slags are gonna lead! As far as ah'm concerned, 
Black Arachnia's leadin' ya tin-horns!"
